  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Virtues Project Fiji</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With the economic impact of covid 19 in Fiji bringing job losses and depression there has been an increase in violence against women and children. The youth, trained with the virtues project and puppets, continue to make a huge impact visiting communities and teaching government officials about how the virtues project operates to change the way people respond to their messages and each other. In recognition the Red cross and other agencies request their voluntary support for their programs.</narrative>
  </description>
